data.description: Opportunity awaits in highly desirable south Salem location! 2000 Built Manufactured home on quiet cul de sac. 3 large bedrooms + office, 2 baths. Tile flooring in Kitchen area. Master bedroom with large walk in closet, dual vanity, garden tub and separate shower. Full appliances in kitchen w/ island, inside utility, single attached garage, large enclosed patio, and fully fenced backyard. Being sold As-Is.
